description: Deletes an Image Builder image resource. This does not delete any EC2 AMIs or ECR container images that are created during the image build process. You must clean those up separately, using the appropriate Amazon EC2 or Amazon ECR console actions, or API or CLI commands.

parameters.name: imageBuildVersionArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Image Builder image resource to delete.

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The request ID that uniquely identifies this request.

nested_items.name: imageBuildVersionArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Image Builder image resource that this request deleted.
